These are Puzzles for 4x3 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-1::.
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: lacrosse, surfing, tennis
There are 3 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, tea, juice
House: futuristic, modern, ranch-style
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: amaryllis, begonia, rose
1. the person who growsamaryllis is on the right of the ranch-style house##1
2. the futuristic house is on the left of the person who growsrose##1
3. the person who's sport is lacrosse is between the person drinking tea and the person drinking juice##2
4. the person who growsamaryllis is on the right of the person who's sport is surfing##1
5. the ranch-style house is the person drinking tea##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |     3     |
| Sport         | surfing | lacrosse   | tennis   |
| Beverage   | tea     | iced-tea | juice |
| House   | ranch-style  | futuristic    | modern      |
| Flower     | begonia     | amaryllis      | rose |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-2::.
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: july, april, june
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: swisher, oliveros, alhambra
3 different games are played: mah-jongg, bridge, whist
City: miami, liverpool, colone
1. the alhambra-smoker is on the left of the person traveling to liverpool##1
2. the person playing whist is on the left of the alhambra-smoker##1
3. the person who's birthday is in april is the person playing whist##1
4. the person who's birthday is in july is the person playing bridge##1
5. the person traveling to miami is between the oliveros-smoker and the person who's birthday is in june##2
6. the person who's birthday is in june is the person traveling to liverpool##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |     3      |
| Birthday          | april  | july     | june     |
| Cigar   | oliveros     | alhambra     | swisher      |
| Game   | whist  | bridge | mah-jongg |
| City           | colone | miami     | liverpool       |

