.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-3::.
3 different games are played: chess, snooker, bridge
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: salsa, disco, electronic
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: aconite, marigold, azalea
There are 3 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, juice, almond-milk
1. the fan salsa is on the left of the person who growsazalea##1
2. the person drinking hot-chocolate is between the fan electronic and the person who growsazalea##2
3. the person playing chess is on the far left##1
4. the person drinking juice is the person playing snooker##1
5. the person drinking hot-chocolate is the person who growsmarigold##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |    3     |
| Game          | chess  | bridge     | snooker     |
| Music-Genre           | electronic | salsa  | disco   |
| Flower   | aconite  | marigold    | azalea |
| Beverage           | almond-milk     | hot-chocolate | juice |

