There are 3 different nationalities: german, pakistani, american
There are 3 different favourite colors: lilac, white, orange
The people have 3 different hobbies: filmmaking, cooking, board-games
1. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the right of the person who likes white##1
2. the palace house is on the right of the american##1
3. the modern house is between the pakistani and the person who likes lilac##2
4. the palace house is the person who's hobby is cooking##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |     2      |     3      |
| House    | victorian       | modern  | palace   |
| Nationality     | pakistani    | american  | german |
| Color     | white   | orange | lilac        |
| Hobby   | board-games | filmmaking     | cooking      |

