2. the tower house is between the person who likes chestnut and the person watching sports movies##2
3. the person watching adventure movies is the gothic-revival house##1
4. the person traveling to edinburgh is on the right of the person traveling to boston##1
5. the tower house is on the left of the person traveling to new-york##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |      3      |
| City          | boston    | edinburgh     | new-york      |
| Movie-Genre         | adventure | crime | sports |
| Color   | chestnut  | amber       | ivory       |
| House           | gothic-revival     | tower       | townhouse     |

