2. the owner of the chinchilla is between the designer and the fan r&b##2
3. the person who growspoppy is on the right of the mechanic##1
4. the fan r&b is on the far right##1
5. the owner of the chinchilla is between the owner of the goat and the person who growsballoon-flower##2

.:: Answer ::.
