3. the person playing snooker is on the left of the person driving the quad-bike##1
4. the dutch is between the person driving the bus and the person playing go##2
5. the person playing snooker is the person watching romance movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |       2       |     3      |
| Game      | mah-jongg       | snooker      | go      |
