The people's birthday is in 3 different months: august, february, january
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: soccer, golf, biathlon
House: farmhouse, gothic-revival, cottage
1. the person who's birthday is in february is between the cottage house and the person who's birthday is in august##2
2. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the right of the cottage house##1
3. the person who's hobby is puzzles is the person who's sport is soccer##1
4. the person who's sport is biathlon is the person who's hobby is baking##1
5. the farmhouse house is the person who's sport is golf##1
6. the person who's birthday is in august is on the right of the gothic-revival house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |    3     |
| Hobby   | puzzles | baking  | card-games     |
| Birthday   | january    | february | august |
| Sport           | soccer        | biathlon   | golf  |
| House     | cottage      | gothic-revival   | farmhouse |

