2. the person who's birthday is in may is on the left of the person who's sport is sailing##1
3. the person drinking juice is the person who's birthday is in august##1
4. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the left of the person drinking milk##1
5. the person drinking fanta is on the far right##1
6. the person who's sport is handball is between the person who's sport is sailing and the dutch##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |    3     |
| Sport           | weightlifting   | handball   | sailing |
| Beverage   | juice | milk   | fanta     |
| Nationality   | dutch     | russian      | australian    |
| Birthday           | august | may | october    |

