There are 3 different nationalities: french, russian, american
There 3 different types of food: mango, nectarine, cherry
1. the person eating nectarine is the american##1
2. the russian is on the left of the person driving the airplane##1
3. the french is between the person who growsaconite and the person driving the motorbike##2
4. the russian is the person eating cherry##1
5. the person eating mango is between the person who growslily and the russian##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |      2      |      3      |
| Flower      | aconite | iris     | lily        |
| Transport         | skateboard   | airplane | motorbike |
| Nationality   | russian        | french       | american      |
