.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-20::.
House: cape-cod, victorian, futuristic
There are 3 different nationalities: malaysian, indonesian, colombian
There are 3 different favourite colors: amber, apricot, red
There are 3 different favourite beverages: sprite, fanta, lemonade
1. the cape-cod house is on the right of the person who likes apricot##1
2. the indonesian is the person drinking sprite##1
3. the person who likes apricot is the person drinking sprite##1
4. the person who likes amber is the futuristic house##1
5. the colombian is between the person drinking lemonade and the person who likes apricot##2
6. the person who likes red is the cape-cod house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |     2     |     3      |
| House        | victorian      | cape-cod | futuristic |
| Nationality         | indonesian     | colombian    | malaysian        |
| Color       | apricot | red   | amber   |
| Beverage   | sprite          | fanta     | lemonade       |

 